doc_prompt = (
    "Please convert the following technical troubleshooting content into **Confluence Storage Format (HTML/XML)** suitable for direct insertion via the Confluence REST API using `representation: storage`.\n\n"
    "Strictly follow these formatting guidelines:\n"
    "1. **Headings:** Use <h2> for main sections (e.g., 'Check Instance Status'), <h3> for sub-sections.\n"
    "2. **Bulleted Lists:** Use <ul><li> for bullet points and nested bullets.\n"
    "3. **Bold Text:** Use <strong> tags.\n"
    "4. **Code Blocks:** Use the Confluence code macro like this:\n"
    "   <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\">\n"
    "     <ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">bash</ac:parameter>\n"
    "     <ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[\n"
    "     your code here\n"
    "     ]]></ac:plain-text-body>\n"
    "   </ac:structured-macro>\n"
    "5. **Inline code:** Use <code>your_code</code> for inline snippets.\n"
    "6. **Links:** Use <a href=\"URL\">text</a>.\n"
    "7. **Preserve All Content:** Do not remove, summarize, or add any information. Retain every word from the original.\n"
    "8. **Output Only the Final HTML Block.** Do not include explanations, headers, or metadata. No YAML, markdown, or commentary.\n\n"
    "Here is the content to be formatted:\n"
    "---\n"
    f"{doc_input}\n"
    "---"
)
